welcome to the boyar value group  boyar value groupboyar value group blog newsroom team contact welcome to the boyar value group the boyar value groups’ mission is to search for value on behalf of our clients since  the boyar family of companies has focused on creating value for our clients — by seeking out and investing in companies whose intrinsic value significantly exceeds that of its current market price we are committed to the idea that through hard work patience and dedication to the core tenets of value investing it is possible to buy a dollar for fifty cents while many fads and gimmicks have come and gone since we started in the investment business we’ve remained steadfast in our belief that value investing is the best way to preserve and create wealth in the long term these core values not only form our philosophy but lie at the heart of what we do both in our money management and institutional research divisions we look forward to putting our knowledge and expertise to work for you boyar asset management boyar research we have been managing money since  utilizing our proprietary inhouse value oriented equity strategy we manage money for high net worth individuals and institutions via separately managed accounts in addition since  we have managed the boyar value fund to serve individuals who cannot meet our minimum investment criteria for separately managed accounts visit boyar asset management  since  we have been producing independent research on intrinsically undervalued companies across the market capitalization spectrum and in a wide variety of industries using a business person’s approach to stock market investing it is interesting to note that since  approximately  of all the companies that have appeared in our flagship publication asset analysis focus have been take over or profitably liquidated visit boyar research  past performance is no guarantee of future results recent posts complimentary research report fro complimentary excerpt from how to b