 the new school for social research the canadian life and health insurance association inc annual investment conference and the new york bankers association among others he also taught a course on mergers and acquisitions at the new school for social research before coming to wall street mr boyar was employed on the audit staff of pricewaterhouse he earned a bs degree from cw post college of long island university in june  and attended suffolk university law school in boston massachusetts since  he has been a member of the new york society of security analysts and the federation of financial analysts mark boyar is a trustee of long island university was formerly chairman of its investment committee and currently sits on that committee which has sole responsibility for selecting investment advisors that manage the university’s endowment boyar teammark boyar jonathan boyar matthew geary cfa patrick jamgocian cfa matthew lombardi joseph mareci cfa boyar blogrecent posts complimentary research report fro complimentary excerpt from how to barron’s interviews the boyar v the boyar value group’s st qua boyar research stock acquired tr receive our free monthly enewsletter please fill out the information below to receive our monthly enewsletter featuring exclusive contentall fields are required first name last name email address please leave this field empty please send me periodic updates for boyar value group products and services ﻿ boyax quote  boyar value fund incthe  bloomberg markets error could not add to watchlist x  watchlist boyar value fund incthe boyaxus nasdaq gm usd   as of  am edt  fund type openend fund wk range     yr return  ytd return  before its here its on the bloomberg terminal learn more previous close  wk range     yr return  ytd return  fund type openend fund objective value broad market asset class focus equity geographic focus us nav on   total assets m usd on   inception date  last dividend on   dividend indicated gross yield  fund managers mark a